data.description: Conveniently located to all services, this home has adequate off-street parking and a very generous fenced and deeply shaded back yard. It has a separate dining room, larger bedrooms and some hardwood floors.  Bathroom was updated by previous owner & has step in shower for easy access.   Lots of opportunity for putting your personal touches on this home.
